d=\"note13b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/adversity?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Несчастье</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"в\" id=\"note13c\" data-full-marker=\"13в\">\n<p data-aid=\"123528738\" id=\"note13c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10?lang=rus#p10\">2 Кор. 12:10</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note14a\" data-full-marker=\"14а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123528739\" id=\"note14a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.12?lang=rus#p12\">Мосия 4:12</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.26-35?lang=rus#p26\">Алма 5:26–35</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/justification-justify?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Оправдание, оправдывать</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note14b\" data-full-marker=\"14б\">\n<p data-aid=\"123528740\" id=\"note14b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/joy?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Радость</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"15\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note15a\" data-full-marker=\"15а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123528741\" id=\"note15a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.27?lang=rus#p27\">У. и З. 38:27</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.20?lang=rus#p20\">49:20</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"16\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note16a\" data-full-marker=\"16а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123528742\" id=\"note16a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/2.3-7?lang=rus#p3\">Алма 2:3–7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note16b\" data-full-marker=\"16б\">\n<p data-aid=\"123528743\" id=\"note16b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/